The office of diversity and inclusion is also very close to this bathroom, and you are unlikely to experience any comment or harassment based on physical appearance.

Additionally, it's very out of the way, and some of the younger employees either don't know it exists or don't bother to clean it, so when it's my turn to clean the bathrooms I make sure to do so thoroughly for this one.
